		<title>狗狗不聽話別急著罵！先搞懂牠不聽的「真正原因」</title>
		<link>https://firenews.com.tw/2025/10/09/%e7%8b%97%e7%8b%97%e4%b8%8d%e8%81%bd%e8%a9%b1%e5%88%a5%e6%80%a5%e8%91%97%e7%bd%b5%ef%bc%81%e5%85%88%e6%90%9e%e6%87%82%e7%89%a0%e4%b8%8d%e8%81%bd%e7%9a%84%e3%80%8c%e7%9c%9f%e6%ad%a3%e5%8e%9f%e5%9b%a0/</link>
		
